,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:42:52.000Z","msg":"今日 本身係一個普天同慶嘅 大日子<br />\n係中華人民共和國 香港特別行政區<br />\n回歸祖國廿二周年<br />\n<br />\n喺昨日下午時分 我見到一眾熱愛香港同國家嘅香港市民<br />\n冒住炎熱嘅天氣上街遊行<br />\n表達自己嘅訴求<br />\n對此 我係感到非常之欣慰<br />\n<br />\n可惜 我最心痛嘅係 喺昨日清晨至深夜<br />\n有一班擾亂香港秩序嘅年輕市民<br />\n佢哋目無法紀噉佔領馬路、衝擊立法會、破壞公物、傷害他人<br />\n不但令本港嘅法治以及立法權受到嚴重損害<br />\n更為好多善良嘅市民、警方同議員造成極大嘅傷害同麻煩......"},{"pid":"41f3cf2b28b94d793c67144816e89a8dd91b8e28","tid":1275301,"uid":271413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:43:56.000Z","msg":"我頭先已經講得好清楚啦冇野補充"},{"pid":"1454e3593ebd806dc54061f91fbb4d222dec1882","tid":1275301,"uid":160051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:44:47.000Z","msg":"柒婆：今次仲唔係暴動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f974c0822519cb7e68666bfb7994bf1c0a2e8e5","tid":1275301,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:44:54.000Z","msg":"林鄭：我好眼瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f8ef3a1d90049652833ae6a618f3b1949e2f9d","tid":1275301,"uid":201434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:45:02.000Z","msg":"仲有表示痛心"},{"pid":"3cdb9af1680712741c2f87be6e91d0462a159e67","tid":1275301,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75f8ef3a1d90049652833ae6a618f3b1949e2f9d","tid":1275301,"uid":201434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:45:02.000Z","msg":"仲有表示痛心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:45:39.000Z","msg":"塊玻璃好貴㗎嘛"},{"pid":"ddc70cfd13c13f61bdc1c67b6c82a17201c95624","tid":1275301,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:45:53.000Z","msg":"估下佢會唔會遲到先啦"},{"pid":"4f370b0f0b0184a6449a71db627ab1f49a9a003c","tid":1275301,"uid":206020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:46:15